author: @Jikooking365
text:
Those hypnotic eyes. That alluring smirk. Attraction personified. Jimin always knows what he's doing. There are beautiful people in the world, ALL the boys being 7 of them, but JIMIN is in a category all his own in life. He has that something about him that pulls you in at first sight, makes you want to, not only  keep looking, but know him personally. His aura is like an ethereal, other-worldly glow inviting you to come closer, look closer, see more. He also has a vulnerability about his character and a purity to his energy that gives him a child-like innocence, even while his sensuality and tactile affinity would usually make a person seem otherwise. He makes you feel things you don't expect, think how you never have before, and allows everyone of all genders, races, religions and social groups, the freedom to fall in love with him, because you can't fight the inevitable. All you can do, is close your eyes, open your heart... and fall.
Thank you ChimChim for bringing all the different people in the world, HERE, to appreciate holistic beauty, together. Linked by our love and appreciation for and of YOU. 
🐥💜💜💜🐥
